Class ResourceCard

  • java.lang.Object
    • gameobjects.GameObject
      • gameobjects.Cards.Card

  • public final class ResourceCard
extends Card
    The resource card from the game. Contains all types of resources the are available in the game. Imports enum ResourceType which defines the type of resource this card represents.
